-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNqlgN.gif&h=f4f769b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/N0s93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FN0s93.png&h=ac1ee20e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關羽雲長自爆兒子關平真名叫趙承斌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/N0y8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FN0y8g.jpg&h=00b693a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關羽雲長早已於2013年兒子剛出生時於討論區徵求改名意見及投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/N0Oft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FN0Oft.jpg&h=2dffcdf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關羽雲長宣布兒子名字於討論區投票的結果及解釋創作靈感來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/N02rG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FN02rG.jpg&h=d426843e&s={SIZE}\" /></div> <br />\n突發！關羽雲長趙岸池唔小心開左前鏡，拍到佢開早霸王post自言自語個樣！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zDFOQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzDFOQ.gif&h=7e2813b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/235830_30ef23821740c3b2c4328cd599a917e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F235830_30ef23821740c3b2c4328cd599a917e5.jpg&h=9753f06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/235831_46fa25199d9b95678495e73a5ad5f2f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F235831_46fa25199d9b95678495e73a5ad5f2f5.jpg&h=f6df46ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/235833_91a904c6b4c4bd6197d6ae481f4c8e31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.